                            <comment id="221933" author="jamesanunez" created="Wed, 28 Feb 2018 16:23:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9872&quot; title=&quot;parallel-scale-nfsv3 test_connectathon: connectathon failed: 1&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9872&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9872&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; has landed to b2_10 tag 2.10.3 and master tag 2.10.56 and it should clear up the &apos;No space left on device&apos; issue. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Additionally, we don&apos;t interop test 2.1 and 2.4 any more. So, let&apos;s close this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
